      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it\u2019s been pampered since day one! Not a scratch in sight, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m so excited for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
