    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and babied it since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and meticulously maintained, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
