    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), featuring the highly desirable 3.8L 9A1 flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This example is equipped with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring a pure analog driving experience. Performance is enhanced by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package Plus, providing variable damping and sharpened throttle mapping. The chassis remains rigid and the paint is flawless, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. A recent DME interrogation confirms zero overrevs in all ranges, and the cooling system has been pressure-tested to ensure thermal integrity. This is a definitive, turnkey example for the serious Porsche technician or collector.",
